three-week low.  Thermal coal for delivery to Amsterdam, Rotterdam or
Antwerp with settlement next year dropped $1.25 cents, or 1
percent, to $126.00 a metric ton at 09:09 a.m. in  London , broker
prices on Bloomberg showed. Thatâ€™s the lowest level since Aug.
22.  Bloomberg tracks data from information supplied by ICAP
